      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "text": "Local Government Emergency   Revolving Bridge Loan",
          "bbox": [
            57.24,
            60.93060000000003,
            434.9547,
            129.93360000000007
          ],
          "fontname": "ZLUMDE+PosterGothicRoundExCondATF-Bold",
          "size": 33.0,
          "color": "#1f2452",
          "is_bold": true,
          "is_italic": false,
          "num_lines": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "The Local Government Emergency Revolving Bridge Loan Program is managed by  FloridaCommerce and provides interest free loans to local governments throughout Florida  that were impacted by federally declared disasters. ",
          "bbox": [
            57.24,
            147.20960000000002,
            546.588,
            190.21760000000006
          ],
          "fontname": "ZLUMDE+ProximaNova-Semibold",
          "size": 12.0,
          "color": "#205d9e",
          "is_bold": false,
          "is_italic": false,
          "num_lines": 3
        },
        {
          "text": "More than $40 million is available to fund governmental operations within these Florida counties and  municipalities and bridge the gap between the time of the disaster and the time additional funding sources or  revenues are secured. “Governmental Operations” includes costs associated with continuing, expanding or  modifying local governmental operations to meet disaster-related needs and includes costs such as, but not  limited to, staff salaries and payroll. ",
          "bbox": [
            57.24,
            201.66960000000006,
            536.4700000000003,
            267.66960000000006
          ],
          "fontname": "ZLUMDE+ProximaNova-Regular",
          "size": 10.0,
          "color": "#424242",
          "is_bold": false,
          "is_italic": false,
          "num_lines": 5
        },
        {
          "text": "Learn more about Local Government   POWERED Emergency Bridge Loans or email:  BY: LocalGovernmentBridge@Commerce.FL.gov",
          "bbox": [
            119.99000000000001,
            297.12960000000004,
            358.0404,
